{{/* Runtime projection of the repo-root deno.json (deploys to ~/.local/bin/deno.json,
     read by Deno when executing the tools). Single control plane: the canonical
     config is the repo-root deno.json; here we project its compilerOptions and the
     lock object. `"./deno.lock"` resolves relative to this file, so at runtime it
     points at ~/.local/bin/deno.lock; `frozen: true` makes Deno read that lock
     without ever rewriting it (the only lock-freeze form deno run honours — the
     flat `frozen` key and DENO_FROZEN env are silently ignored), which stops the
     runtime tools racing chezmoi's change tracking. The root's workspace key is
     deliberately dropped — a workspace member key at a leaf dir makes Deno
     hard-error trying to resolve the member path. */ -}}
{{- $root := include "../deno.json" | fromJson -}}
{{ dict "lock" (dig "lock" dict $root) "compilerOptions" (dig "compilerOptions" dict $root) | toPrettyJson }}
